Leopold feels helpless and locks all the doors,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:43.440 --> 00:11:47.040
hoping that this would buy him enough time to&nbsp;
think of something. He shouts to Uhl that all&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:50.560
