The newly promoted Uhl walks down the&nbsp;
street, and a child approaches him;&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:58.960 --> 00:12:02.720
he gives him a document that explains the&nbsp;
mechanism behind the orange tree trick.&nbsp;&nbsp;

