00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:14.320
Uhl experiences a moment of revelation&nbsp;
as he pieces everything together.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:18.560
From the beginning, Eisenheim had planned all of&nbsp;
