00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:23.920
ensuring the success of his plan. The gemstones&nbsp;
he grabbed when he borrowed Leopold's sword,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:23.920 --> 00:12:27.360
the old man he was talking to who happened to be&nbsp;
the doctor that examined Sophie, and up to the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:27.360 --> 00:12:31.680
faking of Sophie's death. Planting all of these&nbsp;
ideas into Uhl's head, making him think that he&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:31.680 --> 00:12:36.000
got close to the truth, not realizing that the&nbsp;
magician was a step ahead of him the entire time.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:39.440
Uhl can't help but laugh and clap to the&nbsp;
unbelievable performance he became a part of.

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:43.120
Eisenheim walks through the meadows&nbsp;
to celebrate with Sophie as they've&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:45.440
